                <p id="rome1">If you want to start 2020 in style – you know the saying – all roads lead to Rome.</p>
                <p id="show1">See more</p>
                <p id="rome2" style="display:none">See out the old 2019 and say hello to 2019 in one of the oldest cities in the world with breath-taking views of amazing sights such as the Colosseum, the Pantheon, Roman Forum and numerous fountains around the city. Hey, while you’re there,
                    why not visit a completely different country – it’s only a couple of metro stops away, you know? We’re talking about the Vatican, of course, where you can see St. Peter’s Basilica and the Sistine Chapel.
                </p>
