                <p id="paris1">Voulez-vous voyager avec nous? The city of love (or lights, whichever works for you) is waiting for you.</p>
                <p id="show2">See more</p>
                <p id="paris2" style="display:none">There is no better place for couples to start 2020 than by walking down the Champs-Elysées, climbing all the way to the top of the Eiffel Tower and warm up in one of the numerous cafes in the Latin Quarter. Bonus – all the amazing museums
                    from Louvre to Pompidou where you can really boost your general knowledge and get those culture Insta points. While there, you can take a trip to Versailles and see how the royals used to live.

                </p>
