                <h2>London</h2>
                <p id="london1">Ready for some 5 o’clock tea? Or 5 AM shot of coffee to push you to keep partying your way into the New Year?</p>
                <p id="show3">See more</p>
                <p id="london2" style="display:none">You might have done it before, but this might be one last massively spectacular pre-Brexit party that London is going to host. Be there an get New Year’s Eve partying done! While you’re not watching the amazing fireworks display around
                    the London Eye and setting your watch to match the banging of Big Ben, you can roam around the city and check out some of the unmissable locations, like the Tower of London, Tower Bridge, Camden Town and Madame Tussauds. Get this trip
                    booked! Now!

                </p>
